            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De simplicitate seu puritate et multiplicitate animi</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P"/>De simplicitate seu puri
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tate / et de multiplicitate 
               <lb ed="#P"/>animi animi capitulum viii:-:-
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Salomon in prouer. ca. iiii.<!--Number unclear--></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e127">protegit 
               <lb ed="#P"/>dominus gradientes simpliciter / simplices per
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>manebunt in terra.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. ix.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e137">Qui ambulat simpliciter
               <lb ed="#P"/>ambulat confidenter</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. xi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e148">Simplicitas iustorum di
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>riget eos Iustitia simplicis diriget 
               <lb ed="#P"/>vias eius / abhominabile est domino cor 
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>prauuum / et voluntas eius in his qui sim
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>pliciter ambulant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. xxii. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e160">Qui diligit cordis mun
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>ditiam propter fructum labiorum suorum habe
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>bit amicum regem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. xxiiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e170">Qui ambulat simp
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>liciter saluus erit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Paralipomenon libro. primo. ca. fi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e180">ait 
               <lb ed="#P"/>dauit scio deus meus quod probes cor
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>da / et simplicitatem diligas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Iesus filius sirach in ecclastico. ca. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e192">Ue duplici corde.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e198"> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. iii. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e200">cor ingrediens duas vias non 
               <lb ed="#P"/>habebit succensus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e207">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e209">Non ventiles te in omnem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ventum / et non eas in omni via. sic enim
               <lb ed="#P"/>peccator probatur in duplici via. denotatio
               <lb ed="#P"/>pessima / est superbia linguem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ouidius epistolarum / epistola. ii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e227">Simplicitas digna fauore fuit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem sine titulo <sic>siue</sic> amorum. libro. iiii. 
               <lb ed="#P"/>et fi:</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e235">Contra nos solos homines natura fuisti
               <lb ed="#P"/>Et nimium damnis ingeniosa tuis</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e243">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Quintilianus declamationum. xvii. de
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>clame. et fi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e247">Bone conscientie simpli
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>citas incauta est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e253">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Mattheus in euangelisto. ca. x.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e257">extote pruden
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tes sicut serpentes et simplices sicut 
               <lb ed="#P"/>columbe.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e263">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Iacobus epistola. primo. ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e267">vir duplex animo 
               <pb ed="#P" n="51-r"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>inconstans / et in omnibus viis suis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum libro. xiii. aliis
               <lb ed="#P"/>xiiii. epistola xiii. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e278">Quod loquemur 
               <lb ed="#P"/>sentiamus. concordet sermo cum vita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Gregorius in pastorali. ca. xxxvi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e288">nichil 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ad defendendum puritate tutius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e294">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Versificator fabularum exopi fabula. iiii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e298">Sepe dolet pictas criminis arte 
               <lb ed="#P"/>capi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e304">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula. xxxviiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e308">Simplicitas veri laus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem fabula. lxii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e316">Qui fine vi sine fraude manent 
               <lb ed="#P"/>hii fraude necantur. Nullo damnan
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tur crimine sepe boni.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e324">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Cato. ca. iiii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e328">Simplicitas veri fraus est fama ficta 
               <lb ed="#P"/>loquendi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-d1e335">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Gualterius de castellione libro. vii.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d26263-Qd1e339">Prodest simplicitas iusto. noceatque 
               <lb ed="#P"/>nocenti:-</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
